              ],
              "dialogueType": "sendNext",
              "text": "The riding for Knights are a bit different from the rides available for regular folks. The takes place through a creature that is of the Mimi race that can be found on this island; they are called #bMimianas#k. Instead of riding monsters, the Knights ride Mimiana. There's one thing that you should never, ever forget."
